      <div class="formula-ref">
        <div class="formula-ref-label">Quick Reference</div>
        <div class="formula-ref-sub">
          Gradient: \(\nabla f=(f_x,f_y)\) &nbsp;·&nbsp;
          Directional deriv: \(D_{\mathbf u}f=\nabla f\cdot\mathbf u\) (\(\mathbf u\) unit) &nbsp;·&nbsp;
          Hessian: \(H=\begin{pmatrix}f_{xx}&f_{xy}\\f_{yx}&f_{yy}\end{pmatrix}\), classify by \(\det H\) and \(f_{xx}\) &nbsp;·&nbsp;
          Chain rule: \(\dfrac{\partial z}{\partial s}=\dfrac{\partial z}{\partial x}\dfrac{\partial x}{\partial s}+\dfrac{\partial z}{\partial y}\dfrac{\partial y}{\partial s}\) &nbsp;·&nbsp;
          Tangent plane: \(z=f(\mathbf x_0)+\nabla f(\mathbf x_0)\cdot(\mathbf x-\mathbf x_0)\)
        </div>
